reviewText: I bought this for my best friend and she was thoroughly impressed and it arrived in a very quick manner.
Boring, but OK if you are her fan. If I could preview before purchase I probably would not have bought it.  it is only good for one viewing.

My son is the biggest Iggy Azalea fan and I got this as a Christmas gift for him. We watched it later and he said it was the worst movie he had ever seen. Well I wouldn't even call it a movie. It was basically just video of a bunch of radio personalities giving Iggy a hard time. Even though it is called "Her Life, Her Story", it barely tells about just that. Please, just spare yourself some time and money by not even buying this. Thank You.
Purchased for my daughter who is an Iggy fan and this video is Totally not what she expected.  Not worth purchasing.
Bought it as a gift for my niece. She loves Iggy! She had a huge smile when she opened it :)
loved them all keep them all coming please and have a happy and wonderful but safe New Year.
